PiperOrigin-RevId: 359944681
Change-Id: I358c71153d4d5ed77fb49647d7209d61e5cf2e18","distinct":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tensorflow/tensorflow/commits/6205301167deac629fb639ff60e140a6043db7bc"},{"sha":"db9ef9a0c0c3d0b4f24d05a097de4955230b6a0e","author":{"name":"Jacques Pienaar","email":"8b5f536c3e2f2b8ae266b27bc9085a584b5bd904@google.com"},"message":"Move pre-export verification to helper function and pass

This enables reusing in a pipeline and so getting an error reproducer if export pipeline doesn't produce expected output. Also change to return errors in context rather than use a status so that we can get more exact errors.

Currently this would result in verifying this invariant 2x, so we could add a ConvertVerifiedModuleToGraph entry point too to avoid this or just during export do it while exporting to avoid walking over the module again.
